        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": "<p>Most of irregular verbs will only be stem-vowel changing, where the vowel in the stem changes in the <b>second and third person singular</b> (du and er/sie/es forms). There are three basic types of vowel change:</p>"
